This internal tabletop exercise is a critical step in strengthening the organization’s ability to respond to real-world security incidents.

By simulating a realistic breach scenario and challenging existing assumptions, the organization can proactively identify and address weaknesses before they are exposed in an actual incident or external evaluation.

